'''Will''' is a minor character in the [[Season 1|first season]]. He is played by [[Bronson Webb]] and only appears in the [[Winter is Coming (episode)|series premiere]]. Will was a [[ranger]] in the [[Night's Watch]] who was executed for [[desertion]] by [[Eddard Stark|Ned Stark]].

